org.polarsys.chess.monitoring.monitoringxml

Interface MonitoredResource

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Resource, Thread
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MonitoredResourceImpl, ResourceImpl, ThreadImpl

    public interface MonitoredResource
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Monitored Resource'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Name
    • Period
    • Executiontime
    • Blockingtime
    • Responsetime

    See Also:
    MonitoringxmlPackage.getMonitoredResource()
